public static interface TableSelect.Predicate.FilterRow<E>

A virtual row which can be filtered. It allows to retrieve the data by column index and ImmutableTable or the ImmutableColumn.ColumnIdentity

Author:
Omnaest

getElement

E getElement(ImmutableColumn.ColumnIdentity<E> columnIdentity,
             int skipNumber)
Similar to #getElement(ColumnIdentity) but skips the given number of matches of the ImmutableColumn.ColumnIdentity to allow resolving ImmutableColumn.ColumnIdentitys which are occurring more than once, too. This is e.g. necessary for self joins, where the same table columns will occur multiple times.

columnIdentity -
skipNumber -
